#
# Precedence: PRINCIPAL-ONLY first (never over-claim delegability), then the
# assistant's own infrastructure, then team domains (need an implementation
# verb AND a domain hit), then the assistant's delegable classes. No match ->
# PRINCIPAL-ONLY.
#
# NOTE: These are EXAMPLE rules. Replace the names, domains, and personal
# keywords with your own.
# =============================================================================

